    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it's hard not to feel like one side has a much more logical foundation. it feels like the school is just following a set of progressive values that they treat as objective truth, whereas the parents' arguments often sound like they're just based on tradition or religion. is there a way to tell which approach is actually better for a child's development, or is it just a matter of who has the more 'modern' view?",
